WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.417 --> 00:00:01.309
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.309 --> 00:00:02.960
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.340 --> 00:00:04.480
Praise the Lord.

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:09.929
I have some things on my heart to talk about that I've been praying over.

00:00:10.304 --> 00:00:19.000
The Lord told me specific things; He said, 'Brandon, you cannot share everything I've been telling you right now.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:31.880
' Folks, we're about to see a great shaking to awaken, and a lot of the body of Christ is not ready; they're not here.

00:00:32.044 --> 00:00:36.860
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I want you to keep bringing the people to me.

00:00:36.860 --> 00:00:42.532
Get ready with the catcher's mitts, for they're coming in hot.

00:00:42.532 --> 00:00:49.020
Be a light in the darkness, for the darkness is about to become even darker.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:01:00.519
You will see in the days ahead things that you never dreamed you were going to see—things that I never dreamed that I was going to see.

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:17.664
' I thought the rapture of the church was going to take place way before all this, and some of the things that the Lord is showing me involve shock and awe.

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:27.998
I've been praying over our new president and his government.

00:01:32.266 --> 00:01:37.606
A lot of people are still focused on the finances, and you're missing it.

00:01:37.606 --> 00:01:47.725
People email me saying, 'Brandon, you told us to invest in this or that,' but I've never told you to invest in anything, not one time.

00:01:54.040 --> 00:02:39.223
I do not watch prophetic videos because I do not want them influencing what I'm hearing from the Holy Spirit myself.

00:02:39.223 --> 00:03:25.531
If you want to jump from prophetic video to prophetic video, that's up to you, but you need to seek God yourself.

00:03:25.531 --> 00:03:57.906
This is not a time to play 'prophet telephone.

00:03:57.906 --> 00:05:14.080
' It's like that game where you whisper something in someone's ear, and by the time it gets back to you, it's something totally different than whenever it left your mouth.

00:05:17.088 --> 00:05:53.423
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I'm about to clean house in a major way.

00:05:53.423 --> 00:06:58.552
' Anyway, the way I saw it in the spirit: the true voices of the Father are going to come up to a higher level in an intimacy that is beyond comprehension.

00:06:58.552 --> 00:07:40.093
Those who are not hearing clearly—who are adding flesh to it or hearing familiar spirits—need to be careful.

00:07:40.093 --> 00:08:33.685
Sometimes it is just your own thoughts, your own mind talking to you, and you're calling it prophetic.

00:08:34.497 --> 00:09:35.187
The Lord showed me this is going to magnify because it requires going vertical, losing yourself in Him, and being desperate for change.

00:09:37.880 --> 00:10:33.009
I watch Billy Burke and Rodney Howard-Browne to fan the flame, to keep being filled so the new wine doesn't turn to vinegar.

00:10:33.009 --> 00:11:22.413
Many are living on five-year-old manna, a five-year-old Rhema word from God, and you're not going from glory to glory.

00:11:22.413 --> 00:12:02.849
The first person I've met recently who has a true prophetic leading was Prophet Joseph Z.

00:12:19.270 --> 00:13:00.260
I don't even want to watch his videos now because I want to keep my hearing of the Holy Spirit separate from his.

00:13:00.260 --> 00:13:32.130
It's about seeking Him; when you knock, the door will be opened.

00:13:32.130 --> 00:14:20.306
I have an urgency to tell you: it's time to get your wood un-wet and fan that flame.

00:14:20.306 --> 00:15:09.267
Arise and shine, for the glory of the Lord is risen upon you.

00:15:09.267 --> 00:15:35.373
It's all hands on deck right now.

00:15:51.759 --> 00:16:10.822
The Lord said He's done with the mixture and the lukewarm.

00:16:10.822 --> 00:16:47.030
Judgment begins in His house first, starting with the leaders and prophetic voices.

00:16:47.040 --> 00:17:18.383
He spoke thunderously about the leadership of the church.

00:17:24.457 --> 00:17:56.133
I had to pull my car over; I felt the holiness of God.

00:17:56.133 --> 00:18:33.039
He said there will be no compromise in His true voices.

00:18:33.039 --> 00:19:00.480
He spoke about people focused on crypto for selfish gain.

00:19:05.248 --> 00:20:07.840
He said 75% of the people on this platform are here for selfish gain, but the other 25% have a true hunger.

00:20:08.190 --> 00:21:03.480
He said as I bring correction, some will leave, and that's okay; He will bring true prayer warriors to fill their positions.

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:37.377
We're about to see the greatest harvest of souls, but first, a shaking to awaken.

00:21:37.377 --> 00:22:14.234
There's a rat within America; I've seen things I can't even go into depth about.

00:22:14.234 --> 00:22:26.325
Get your house in order.

00:22:26.325 --> 00:22:42.910
Think 'Red Dawn' and watch Cuba.

00:22:54.967 --> 00:23:00.088
The last administration was corrupt and allowed criminal things.

00:23:00.088 --> 00:23:29.426
We're about to see shaking in the heavens—asteroids and signs that humans can't control.

00:23:29.426 --> 00:23:50.964
When they call 'peace and safety,' sudden destruction will come.

00:23:50.964 --> 00:24:14.728
We must pray for President Trump to have supernatural discernment and wisdom.

00:24:14.728 --> 00:24:25.749
Tariffs on Canada and Mexico...

00:24:25.749 --> 00:24:43.795
there's something wrong in the atmosphere.

00:24:43.795 --> 00:25:18.200
The trucks, the vans, the planes—it's time to come up higher in your discernment.

00:25:18.200 --> 00:25:41.885
Over the past four years, very evil people have crossed the border.

00:25:43.368 --> 00:26:16.177
In a 24-hour period, everything you know as stability will change.

00:26:16.177 --> 00:26:47.893
9/11 and COVID changed the world in a day; listen to what's coming.

00:26:47.893 --> 00:27:00.980
Take your eyes off your pocketbook and look vertical.

00:27:00.980 --> 00:27:05.671
Fast and pray.

00:27:11.845 --> 00:27:58.620
I will have to stand alone on some things I say, but in time they will prove accurate.

00:27:58.620 --> 00:28:18.792
Focus on protecting your household and hearing Him for yourself.

00:28:18.792 --> 00:29:00.415
He said, 'They're coming in hot, Brandon, and you've got to have your catcher's mitts on.

00:29:00.415 --> 00:29:27.240
' After 9/11, everyone ran to church, but many found a lukewarm gospel.

00:29:32.655 --> 00:29:45.310
This time, they will run to you, the 25%.

00:29:45.310 --> 00:29:58.840
Be that vessel God can use.

00:29:58.840 --> 00:30:56.359
What I've seen in the last 48 hours has shaken me; I've been told not to speak it publicly as it would put my family in danger.

00:30:56.359 --> 00:31:23.926
Focus on His face to know what's needed for your house.

00:31:23.926 --> 00:31:40.440
Regarding finances, the enemy wants to shake you out.

00:31:45.800 --> 00:32:10.440
You must hear His voice like the ticking of a clock.

00:32:23.680 --> 00:32:47.127
I warned you about the chickens back in 2022, and look at the egg shortages now.

00:32:47.127 --> 00:32:51.120
Pray about what I'm telling you.

00:32:51.120 --> 00:33:34.372
Seek Him daily, fast something like social media or coffee, and put Him first.

00:33:34.372 --> 00:34:14.462
I've been instructed I can't say certain things, but I want to take communion with y'all.

00:34:14.462 --> 00:34:33.760
Remember: 'Red Dawn' and the rats inside.

00:34:43.580 --> 00:34:53.725
Pray for the President's discernment; handle the bear with care.

00:34:53.725 --> 00:35:01.986
Father, we thank You.

00:35:01.986 --> 00:35:04.455
Our desire is to fall more in love with You.

00:35:04.455 --> 00:35:15.020
I pray for the 25% here.

00:35:15.020 --> 00:35:38.180
We'll do live prayer for the planes and other events.

00:35:45.730 --> 00:36:12.926
We thank You, Lord, for the body of Jesus and Your stripes that heal us.

00:36:23.600 --> 00:36:41.359
We apply the blood of Jesus over our homes, marriages, and finances.

00:36:41.359 --> 00:36:58.387
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

00:36:58.387 --> 00:37:15.618
We apply the blood over our families and churches.

00:37:24.831 --> 00:37:36.068
We hear Your voice, and a stranger's we will not follow.

00:37:55.460 --> 00:37:55.905
You are the miracle-working God.

00:37:57.780 --> 00:38:00.090
You deserve the glory and the honor, Lord.

00:38:00.090 --> 00:38:39.440
We lift our hands in worship as we bless Your holy name.

00:39:03.430 --> 00:39:10.635
For You are great; You do miracles so great.

00:39:10.635 --> 00:39:16.227
There is no one else like You.

00:39:16.227 --> 00:40:05.880
We're about to see something we've never seen before.

00:40:05.880 --> 00:41:40.008
I'm thankful the Lord chose us to be born into this generation for such a time as this.

00:41:40.008 --> 00:42:40.613
Labor pains will get more intense in the days ahead, but the glorious church will rise.

00:42:40.613 --> 00:43:01.688
I bless your finances and supplies.

00:43:15.150 --> 00:43:18.594
I believe for supernatural harvest and health.

00:43:32.125 --> 00:43:37.120
We are rooted and grounded in Him.

00:43:37.120 --> 00:43:53.499
God is a god of abundant supply.

00:44:12.319 --> 00:44:14.784
I hope this blessed and shook you.

00:44:14.784 --> 00:44:37.000
Check out our other channels in the description.

00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:53.720
Like and subscribe to help the algorithm.

00:44:53.720 --> 00:45:01.475
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart because Jesus loves you.

00:45:01.475 --> 00:45:09.520
Relationship, not religion.

00:45:09.520 --> 00:45:09.880
God bless you all.

00:45:09.880 --> 00:45:13.200
Bye-bye.
